videos.headline: Childers finds Tears for 10-yard TD
videos.description: Marcus Childers hits Spencer Tears in the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Johnson intercepts Bollas
videos.description: George Bollas' pass gets intercepted by Northern Illinois' Jawuan Johnson.

videos.headline: Kent State responds, gets INT of their own
videos.description: Kent State answers Northern Illinois' interception when Jerrell Foster intercepts Daniel Santacaterina's pass in the end zone.

videos.headline: Lurry returns INT 45 yards
videos.description: Shawun Lurry intercepts Dustin Crum's pass and cuts across the field on his 45-yard return.

videos.headline: Wimann catches and runs for 25-yard TD
videos.description: Marcus Childers finds a wide open Shane Wimann who runs into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Kent State muffs punt
videos.description: Raymond James is unable to fair catch punt, recovered by Alex Schwab for Northern Illinois.

videos.headline: Childers hits Huff for 2-yard TD
videos.description: Marcus Childers extends Northern Illinois' lead with a 2-yard touchdown pass to Jordan Huff.
